{"tid":1638523,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解一定要港島遊行?","createTime":"2019-10-08T10:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T11:29:48.000Z","uid":5271,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e3d9244c57933c1a3bf08990eb65a35de7acd028","tid":1638523,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:40:59.000Z","msg":"點解百萬遊行一定要限死港島？<br />\n我哋可以仿照10.4 咁開花，不過和理非版<br />\n每區點算人數再加埋<br />\n仲可以講埋港共打壓遊行，迫住各區遊行<br />\n<br />\n目標係上國際新聞<br />\n臨近人權法，要行一次俾美國睇<br />\n<br />\n有唔少優點：<br />\n1. 交通方便<br />\n2. 安全<br />\n3. 分散狗力<br />\n4. 熟識地形<br />\n5. 時間短<br />\n6. 街坊輕鬆參加<br />\n<br />\n*建議可以先定集合地方，而路線到時先be water<br />\n盡量避免同狗接觸，甚至淨係搞集會"},{"pid":"8f87e8bec93d465d05ba448a7a6d8ccf720eb927","tid":1638523,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02d0ee2044ba6f3f214594285fa883973c6eb97e","tid":1638523,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:41:34.000Z","msg":"推到200 萬遊行再現"},{"pid":"8094550dd58a7d0140af9da606db8a20e9cf1482","tid":1638523,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:41:43.000Z","msg":"正視聽！等7日？真實嘅「人權民主法案」日程表<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ekdRzS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ekdRzS</a>"},{"pid":"acda45a9730f167634178d2680bfab640062a9c6","tid":1638523,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f509c6f6c4e4a45d0a2b6199ac2937e2bae33d","tid":1638523,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:42:05.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cbeff8543442e23b2259e4dbd5af4b6f982b036f","tid":1638523,"uid":4875,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:42:30.000Z","msg":"因為民陣唔識變通"},{"pid":"a037d6e283cd9f7f69c3f2f7d8fd6ebd0c115336","tid":1638523,"uid":73915,"like":0